    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Micropsalliota suricatoides: (a) basidiomata in situ (LE F-348072, holotype), (b) pilei with umbo (LE F-348069), (c) pileus with umbo (LE F-348070, photo N.V. Psurtseva), (d) basidiospores, (e) basidia, (f) cheilocystidia, (g) pileipellis hyphae. Bars: a–c = 1 cm; d–f = 10 μm; g = 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10212921/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

